   <text:p text:style-name="First_20_paragraph"><text:line-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Qui suscite la Juive et les sept Machabées,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Et, quand Jeanne a saisi nos bannières tombées,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Du sacre et du bûcher lui montre les chemins.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:line-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P24">Lux.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ô République universelle,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">L’astre n’est encor qu’étincelle ;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mais, pareille au soleil joyeux,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Couvrant les Paris et les Romes,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tu seras la clarté des hommes,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Comme il est la clarté des cieux.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
