   <text:p text:style-name="P76"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Couverture de l’édition originale. — </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">À un voyageur</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T5">, frontispice de l’édition originale (Tony Johannot). — </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">L’Aumône</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T5"> (Alfred Johannot).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P76"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fac-similé : </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">À M. Louis B.</text:span></text:p>
