   <text:p text:style-name="P99"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Couverture de l’édition originale. — </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">À des oiseaux envolés</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T5">, dessin de Victor Hugo. — Portrait du Général Hugo. — Portraits de Madame Victor Hugo (Louis Boulanger). — Adèle Hugo, Charles Hugo, crayons de M</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">me</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T5"> Victor Hugo. — Léopoldine, François-Victor, crayons de M</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">me</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T5"> Victor Hugo. — </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">À Albert Dürer</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T5"> (Steinhel).</text:span></text:p>
